kgmoji\" /><br />\n寫明三個月就三個月㗎啦<br />\n提早結束又冇補水係唔合理喎<br />\n仲話咩日本係咁㗎啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家申請人又唔係要即刻出發<br />\n想要返個可以延期嘅保障啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"香港人最鍾意屌自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c240a459eaa4a2a239de3d1c322e4b74d6adb499","tid":1924363,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3105a100160ab6f7ca7b8c832a86c5229a2364f","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c6bcb60448e7456538082af8ccf80833c0078fc","tid":1924363,"uid":268516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"假設成功如期去到<br />\n真係仲有野可以work?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"冇 所以最好就係俾人取消申請<br />\n下年再俾佢地申請過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"係就講清楚訴求係再申請過<br />\n一陣日本真係傻更更肯放佢地而家過去<br />\n真係玩鳩自己"},{"pid":"265a3f00616f69d555e8a5a9f79cf70364cc3a1e","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"而家全球大爆<br />\n應該去其他地方wh嘅都有同樣問題"},{"pid":"ec0924c0d1f8ef13392f808083f5b1c239cab386","tid":1924363,"uid":10241,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"應該要延期啦<br />\n有時唔係話拎完個visa就可以即刻出發<br />\n我幾年前都申請到,出左結果先辭職<br />\n再拎個visa後搵工到搵地方住<br />\n仲要成年唔係香港好多野要處理<br />\n當年我係臨最尾2果日先過日本<br />\n<br />\n依家又唔係申請人問題<br />\n係武漢肺炎同個政策問題<br />\n點解有d人會鬧班申請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64e5f54bdf42244dbc6a77c7a64aac96f36d0f6","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec0924c0d1f8ef13392f808083f5b1c239cab386","tid":1924363,"uid":10241,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"應該要延期啦<br />\n有時唔係話拎完個visa就可以即刻出發<br />\n我幾年前都申請到,出左結果先辭職<br />\n再拎個visa後搵工到搵地方住<br />\n仲要成年唔係香港好多野要處理<br />\n當年我係臨最尾2果日先過日本<br />\n<br />\n依家又唔係申請人問題<br />\n係武漢肺炎同個政策問題<br />\n點解有d人會鬧班申請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"個個屌自己人就以為高人一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6834b588059451c191c2087d10f8df425b00a7a0","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"連登崇日撚快啲仆入嚟屌埋香港人一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77708af25548a5147c800ce07c27d27abccfb81b","tid":1924363,"uid":34107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"件事完左先講啦<br />\n不過特登辭工果班就真係慘"},{"pid":"ef5ff00848e5215e36b9a8876ff4bd82ac39899b","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77708af25548a5147c800ce07c27d27abccfb81b","tid":1924363,"uid":34107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"件事完左先講啦<br />\n不過特登辭工果班就真係慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"下 實要辭工㗎喎<br />\n有咩工可以停薪留職一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ec0c0b3cd620a0a962ce26753f0857463e1d3c","tid":1924363,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef5ff00848e5215e36b9a8876ff4bd82ac39899b","tid":1924363,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77708af25548a5147c800ce07c27d27abccfb81b","tid":1924363,"uid":34107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"件事完左先講啦<br />\n不過特登辭工果班就真係慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"下 實要辭工㗎喎<br />\n有咩工可以停薪留職一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"有啲大公司有"},{"pid":"6a9cdbea1